{"tid":667832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"石棺藏屍】主審法官急病需治療 高院宣布解散陪審團","createTime":"2018-05-17T05:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T05:46:51.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5941bb5d4d1b96e08eff004558b4d7cf785a52e1","tid":667832,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:38:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180517&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58202537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180517%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58202537&d=c28YW418mKV8lj%2FngD5pWzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8212419e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180517%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58202537&h=d11cb74e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180517&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58202537</a><br />\n<br />\n【石棺藏屍】主審法官急病需治療 高院宣布解散陪審團<br />\n<br />\n荃灣DAN6工廈石棺藏屍案於高院審訊達27天，控方早前已完成舉證，首被告曾祥欣正接受盤問。惟案件今早開庭時，高院法官彭寶琴向控辯各方透露，因為主審法官李瀚良患病需要緊急治療，短期內未能出席聆訊，經商討後各方同意解散陪審團。<br />\n<br />\n彭官提醒陪審團指由於案件需排期重審，吩咐他們不要與其他人討論案件，包括不要在社交媒體等、或面對面與他人談及案件，並感謝他們過去多天對案件的參與。<br />\n<br />\n控辯雙方對李官生病一事毫不知情，當彭官從內庭步出法官席時，大家均露出愕然表情。"},{"pid":"0a4540806faa1c9cdb33dd3430fad202a20bbeec","tid":667832,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060ca1577b11d90891edee48ef4bb929147cb38c","tid":667832,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"額外律師費點計？"},{"pid":"d81dd091a2acd7edeb959f9338e0e15a5437790a","tid":667832,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"又可以心理折磨小草條臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" 